      "solution": "n: int = int(input())\n\noperations: list[int] = []\n\nwhile n != 1:\n    odd = n & 1\n    operations.append(odd)\n    n = (3 * n + 1 if odd else n) >> 1\n    \nprint(*reversed(operations), sep='\\n')",
